<F P=100> Northeast Asia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hosokawa Lays Wreath at Monument </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2003080894 Beijing XINHUA in English 0734 GMT 20 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2003080894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


