<H3> <TI>   Shandong Reports Progress in Economic Development Zones </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1603094894 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1603094894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Summary] Thus far, eight cities and prefectures and 56 
counties in the province, accounting for about 40 percent of the 
province's total territory, have joined the business of coastal 
economic development zones, and 40 percent of Shandong citizens 
have been involved in these zones. Meanwhile, 65 countries and 
regions in the world have made investments in Shandong. A group 
of large, well-known transnational corporations have invested in 
the province for further development. 

</TEXT>

