Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by station reporter Chen Lei -- recorded] </F>
  [Excerpts] With all items on the agenda fulfilled, the 
seven-day second session of the Seventh Hubei Provincial 
Committee of the Chinese People Political Consultative 
Conference [CPPCC] concluded successfully at Wuchang's Hongshan 
Auditorium this morning. [passage omitted] 
  Sitting on the front row of the rostrum at the concluding 
